info.name: Cards API Service
info.description: Provides APIs to read and write credit card related data (such as accounts and transactions) within SAP Concur Expense

item.name: Create new credit card accounts as bulk operation

request.description:
This API creates multiple credit card accounts in an asynchronous manner. Assuming the request is properly authorized and the request body is valid, the API returns 202 (Request Accepted) and processes the request asynchronously. Each account is identified by externalId which needs to be unique. If at least one account of the bulk request fails the validation (e.g. invalid enum or missing required field) the complete request will be rejected with response code 400. A maximum of 1000 accounts are allowed to be sent in one request. Possible error codes:
  • invalidRequest: The request contains errors (usually contains a detailed error list)
  • invalidJson: The request body is not a valid JSON

response.name: The request is not authenticated. Missing or invalid authorization header.

item.name: Retrieve a bulk request by ID

request.description:
Authentication is done via company JWT with required scope cards.bulkrequest.read. 
The appId of the JWT needs to match the appId which created the bulk request.

response.name: The request is not authenticated. Missing or invalid authorization header.
The requested bulk request does not exist

item.name: Create new credit card transactions as bulk operation

request.description:
This API creates multiple credit card transactions in an asynchronous manner. Assuming the request is properly authorized and the request body is valid, the API returns 202 (Request Accepted) and processes the request asynchronously. Each transaction is identified by externalId which needs to be unique. If at least one item of the bulk request fails the validation (e.g. invalid enum or missing required field) the complete request will be rejected with response code 400. A maximum of 1000 transactions are allowed to be sent in one request. Possible error codes:
  • invalidRequest: The request contains errors (usually contains a detailed error list)
  • invalidJson: The request body is not a valid JSON

response.name: The request is not authenticated. Missing or invalid authorization header.
